            "title": "藍田小巴直剷行人路 撞毀欄杆燈柱 兩人受傷",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"藍田小巴直剷行人路 撞毀欄杆燈柱 兩人受傷\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ae6bb489c7cc6b6c2b505208b64b9d74/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250402/_2025040221121846320.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">藍田小巴直剷行人路 撞毀欄杆燈柱 兩人受傷</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>觀塘鯉魚門道往油塘方向近藍田港鐵站對出行人路，今日（4月2日）晚上7時許，一部綠色專線小巴意外剷上行人路，兩名男女被波及受輕傷，並有約5米欄杆及燈柱被撞毀。救護員接報趕至，將傷者送聯合醫院治理。\n\n</p>\n<p>網上片段所見，小巴懷疑由進入鯉安苑停車場支路的過路處剷上行人路，前行約50米始停下，有傷者坐地接受救援。意外原因仍在調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173899/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一部綠色專線小巴意外剷上行人路。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b64cedad7dc5530ed9d28a8547313322/2025-04/487833423_10236136042161610_5060210927404818486_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一部綠色專線小巴意外剷上行人路。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173903/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一部綠色專線小巴意外剷上行人路。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/14d6a516cf3e2e122aaee38afd839f5d/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-02-21h06m49s681.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一部綠色專線小巴意外剷上行人路。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173902/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"傷者坐地待救。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2d162cee428f3c6dd201dde1e185c03f/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-02-21h07m02s248.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        傷者坐地待救。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173901/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"傷者坐地待救。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b6cd9d84d9095fb7bf0b0ad4f9b8e252/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-02-21h07m16s383.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        傷者坐地待救。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173900/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場交通受阻。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ebac5d33e6c7771fb85534053ef4be89/2025-04/487796527_10236136044681673_2741982468295024123_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場交通受阻。FB：馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
